etal building blocks.  His enduring message emphasizes dignity and opportunity for all people.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-nelson-mandela-a-nation-should-not-be-judged-by-how-it-treats-its-highest-citizens-but/articleshow/132336217.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-nelson-mandela-a-nation-should-not-be-judged-by-how-it-treats-its-highest-citizens-but/articleshow/132336217.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T23:41:04+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132336292,imgsize-82915.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Microsoft defends Asha Sharma, says she is an American CEO and Xbox layoff had nothing to do with H-1B]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132335655.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/microsoft-defends-asha-sharma-says-she-is-an-american-ceo-and-xbox-layoff-had-nothing-to-do-with-h-1b/articleshow/132335655.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/microsoft-defends-asha-sharma-says-she-is-an-american-ceo-and-xbox-layoff-had-nothing-to-do-with-h-1b/articleshow/132335655.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T23:17:40+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132335854,imgsize-70486.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Typhoon Bavi makes landfall in eastern China, over 1 million evacuated]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132334802.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/typhoon-bavi-makes-landfall-in-eastern-china-over-1-million-evacuated/articleshow/132334802.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/typhoon-bavi-makes-landfall-in-eastern-china-over-1-million-evacuated/articleshow/132334802.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T22:35:16+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132334815,imgsize-1601216.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Trump threatens Iran with '1000 missiles' as both sides shoot their mouth in Gulf spat]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132334422.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[President Trump threatened Iran with massive missile strikes if assassination plots are pursued. This warning dramatically escalated tensions between the two nations. Disagreements over a maritime deal's interpretation fueled renewed military exchanges. Iran vowed revenge for past actions and perceived US treaty violations. Ambiguity and mistrust now threaten another fragile understanding between them.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-threatens-iran-with-1000-missiles-as-both-sides-shoot-their-mouth-in-gulf-spat/articleshow/132334422.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-threatens-iran-with-1000-missiles-as-both-sides-shoot-their-mouth-in-gulf-spat/articleshow/132334422.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-11T22:12:31+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Chidanand Rajghatta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132334525,imgsize-944959.cms"/></item></channel></rss>